## State

- **Quiz:** step index (URL-driven), answers array, persist to Supabase on each step, auto-resume on return.
- **Coach search:** filters (rating range, price, timezone, style tags), sort, paginated.
- **Booking:** draft → confirmed (Stripe hold) → delivered (coach marks complete) → released (48h auto-release or student confirms). Refund window starts at delivered.
- **Theme:** `light` | `dark`, default `dark`, persisted to cookie so SSR matches.

## Motion tokens (see `tokens.json` → motion)

- `reveal`: 900ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.7, 0.2, 1), translateY(24px → 0) + opacity 0 → 1. Triggered on viewport intersection (threshold 0.12) or if already in viewport on mount.
- `mesh-drift`: 22–28s ease-in-out infinite alternate. Three blobs with different keyframes (`a`, `b`, `c`). Blur 80px.
- `scene-rotate`: 24s on the hero 3D stack parent. `rotateX(14→20)` `rotateY(-16→18)`.
- `float-a/b/c`: 7s/9s/11s ease-in-out infinite alternate — small Y translations on stack children, preserving their individual Z.
- `ticker`: 40s linear infinite, `translateX(0 → -50%)`.
- `shimmer`: 6s linear infinite, background-position `0% → 200%`.
- `gauge-sweep`: 3s cubic-bezier(0.3, 0.7, 0.2, 1) — stroke-dashoffset sweep on circle fill.

